### 12.JS 对象转 url 查询字符串
```
const objectToQueryString = (obj)
                         => Object.keys(obj).map((key)                          
                         =>`${encodeURIComponent(key)}
                         =${encodeURIComponent(obj[key])}`).join('&'); 
objectToQueryString({name: 'Jhon', age: 18, address: 'beijing'}) 
// name=Jhon&age=18&address=beijing 
